dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.backend
Class ValidationResult

java.lang.Object
  dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.backend.ValidationResult

public class ValidationResult
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements the results of a validation returned by AbstractBackend.doValidate(). A ValidationResult maps an APIOperationStatus to the memento that caused the problem.
